                <div class="text-3xl mb-4" aria-hidden="true">üéØ</div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">What I'm Up To</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                  Currently crafting amazing experiences at Indeed, but always excited to hear about new opportunities and collaborations!
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2" role="list" aria-label="Areas of expertise">
                  <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" role="listitem">Product Management</span>
