          <p class="text-gray-600">
            I specialise in iOS app development with Swift, and product management. 
            I work on projects ranging from sports applications like BoxingScorecard to business tools and consumer apps.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Do you work remotely?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Yes, I work remotely and am available for projects worldwide. I'm comfortable with various 
            communication tools and time zone coordination.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">What's your typical project timeline?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Project timelines vary depending on scope and complexity. A typical mobile app project can take 
            3-6 months from concept to launch, while smaller features or consulting projects may take weeks.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">How do you handle project communication?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            I believe in transparent and regular communication. I provide weekly updates, use project 
            management tools, and am always available for questions and feedback throughout the process.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
